data.description: Come take a look at this Portage gem! This charming tri-level home boasts with three bedrooms, two bathrooms, a detached garage, and a fenced yard. Not only is this home cozy, it offers the convenience nearby shopping and restaurants. Also included in this home, you will see, Anderson triple and double pane windows and doors, 5 year old siding, and 7 year old roof. (Sellers are offering $3,000 in seller's concessions for flooring.)
